{"tid":1635583,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中毒煙，再咳過 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-10-07T14:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:11:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dbcdd36cbc08a61373dc0985b0ed096bc7dc6e2a","tid":1635583,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191007/20782086/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F20782086%2F&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=fbcad92f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F20782086%2F&h=f5eaa2bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191007/20782086/</a><br />\n<br />\n中毒煙，再咳過 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191007/large/1570349319_7267.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570349319_7267.jpg&h=b09ab18e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人誰沒捱過催淚煙？總之18區無一倖免，幾千發的催淚彈，彈殼拾起成堆，都放射2014、2015年過期含山埃毒氣，不但嗆鼻催淚還有後遺症。<br />\n<br />\n但避無可避，因為示威現場、地鐵內外、大街小巷、民居、商場、公園&hellip;&hellip;都毒氣熏天，濫權警暴，隨意報復式發洩式向市民近距離放射，殘留物滲在縫隙雨落不散，人人呼吸系統受損。<br />\n<br />\n我們久咳不癒的受害人，已盡量藥療食療，什麼川貝枇杷鱷魚肉湯、南北杏雪梨雪耳荸薺湯、太子參百合瘦肉湯&hellip;&hellip;豬肉枱有時供應新鮮豬肺，可以煲杏汁金銀菜豬肺湯，誰知因豬瘟缺貨，豬肉佬還道：「冇靚肺，豬肺仲貴過人肺。」──對，港人的肺多賤！那18歲中五學生健仔，還遭黑警當胸開槍（一或兩槍待查證），射中肺部，僅距心臟3cm，重傷深切治療，還被插贓嫁禍。<br />\n<br />\n前一陣到台北換換空氣舒緩一下，清粥小菜、杏仁茶、楊桃汁，大量水果，特別是老欉麻豆文旦大豐收，堅實清甜柚子芳香，有止咳化痰潤肺清腸之效，中秋「辭水」變軟後更好吃，狂吃療癒──不過心理上還是抑鬱怨憤的，逃不掉手機動新聞。<br />\n<br />\n回港未幾禁蒙面惡法，在地鐵外行人路又中黑警毒煙，連日逃不掉。再咳過&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"c225fe7b109dbb724743e71d191065ee5cab43e9","tid":1635583,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:11:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=e16d44d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"}]}